2. cs.MS (Mathematical Software) - The paper may involve the use of mathematical software for simulations and analysis of the proposed STBC. 
3. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - STBC is a signal processing technique, and the paper may involve signal processing algorithms and techniques. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - MIMO systems are used in wireless communication networks, and the paper may involve networking and internet architecture aspects. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper may involve computational techniques and algorithms for the design and analysis of the proposed STBC.
